{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293837, "create_time": 1657784597, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我觉得是要让普通岗位也能让人体面生活", "timestamp": 1657784597}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293845, "create_time": 1657784852, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "教育资源不足是根本问题，另外我觉得音乐体育美术不如哲学心理阅读...\n", "timestamp": 1657784852}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293981, "create_time": 1657789105, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "中国根本没钱把素质教育的这些东西让村镇孩子享受", "timestamp": 1657789105}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293991, "create_time": 1657789211, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "我觉得还是先把基层的老师水平提上来要紧。清华附中招的老师都快非清本博士不要了，而小镇的老师可能自己就是个大专水平。这才是真正的差别", "timestamp": 1657789211}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294015, "create_time": 1657789401, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "你提的“音乐”“美术”赛道，全都是要钱才能堆出来的，这对小镇做题家更不公。\n“体育”这条道，对于一些不用钱的项目，其实有人走的。跳水冠军全红婵就是例子。但是但凡花点钱，就又是死路一条。", "timestamp": 1657789401}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294024, "create_time": 1657789612, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "洞主理想可能很美好，让基层的（或者更直白说就是穷人）能够有机会接触更加丰富的教育，有更多选择的路。\n但是！！！！！！\n仅个人看法。这些路比起“做题”而言，更不适合村镇的孩子。反而这些路的拓宽，会侵占掉他们原来可能靠“做题”得到的出路", "timestamp": 1657789612}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294142, "create_time": 1657794271, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "大力兴办职业教育学校，提升职业工人技术水平", "timestamp": 1657794271}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294149, "create_time": 1657794490, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 职业工人待遇上不去再怎么兴办也没用", "timestamp": 1657794490}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294150, "create_time": 1657794517, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "现在的职校办的都是什么东西，一塌糊涂一无是处", "timestamp": 1657794517}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294153, "create_time": 1657794666, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "产业升级需要国家政策补贴，更需要企业家自己转型，如果职工市场一直不缺低价低水平技工企业有什么意愿转型，如果职工市场一直缺少高水平技工企业又凭什么转型", "timestamp": 1657794666}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294155, "create_time": 1657794766, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 职业工人待遇不是国家定的，是市场定的", "timestamp": 1657794766}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294164, "create_time": 1657795419, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 体制内外二元福利是市场定的还是国家定的？", "timestamp": 1657795419}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294165, "create_time": 1657795439, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "职校待了几年什么也没学会还在厕所生了个孩子，相关领导就不感到惊悚汗颜吗。培养几个会写论文的本科生远没有培养几个高水平数控车工重要，职业教育一塌糊涂甚至根本不重视职业教育才是中国教育最大的问题", "timestamp": 1657795439}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294170, "create_time": 1657795581, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 体制内才能容纳多少人？有总人数十分之一吗", "timestamp": 1657795581}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294176, "create_time": 1657795808, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 土地出让金到了谁手里？", "timestamp": 1657795808}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294177, "create_time": 1657795841, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 别忘了房地产可是中国gdp的大头", "timestamp": 1657795841}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294179, "create_time": 1657795888, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 政府用土地出让金搞基建和我说的有什么关系？", "timestamp": 1657795888}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294180, "create_time": 1657795916, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 房地产和你找工作有什么关系", "timestamp": 1657795916}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294366, "create_time": 1657802699, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "在《乌合之众》中已经把小镇做题家的问题讲的很清楚了，中国的教育就是在教出一群极易对体制不满的人。把科举和拉丁教育相混合，制造出的是一小部分卷入体制的做题家和大部分对现状不满的做题家。今天的做题家们与清末新式教育培养出的大量无所适从的学生何其相似。", "timestamp": 1657802699}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294549, "create_time": 1657809559, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "笑死，做题是最不容易作弊的了，其它的太主观\n", "timestamp": 1657809559}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294551, "create_time": 1657809624, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "关系户优势已经很大了，这是想让他们优势更大呗\n", "timestamp": 1657809624}], "create_time": 1657783475, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657809624, "likenum": 13, "n_attentions": 13, "n_comments": 21, "pid": 82995, "poll": {"answers": [{"option": "支持", "votes": 27}, {"option": "反对", "votes": 23}, {"option": "🍉", "votes": 17}], "vote": null}, "reply": 21, "text": "解决“小镇做题家”现象的方法，不是将做题家的地位抬到最高，将选拔性考试成绩高低作为划分人三六九等的手段。而是要将音乐、体育、美术等等资源让村镇的孩子也能享受，扩大一个人可以选择的赛道。", "timestamp": 1657783475}}